== These are not Japanese phrases! ==

These are English phrases that have been translated too literally into Japanese. If you want to sound like a complete foreigner, by all means. But don't be offended when the Japanese person laughs. It's hard not to!

{{WikiProject Languages}}

== words ==
tsukareta and shindoi don't really mean the 100% same thing. Shindoi is used to make it stronger.

